summary: "Okay, let’s do this one last time, yeah? For real this time. This is it. My name is Miles Morales. I was bitten by a...
body: “Okay, let’s do this one last time, yeah? For real this time. This is it. My name is Miles Morales. I was bitten by a radioactive spider, and for like two days, I’ve been the one and only Spider-Man. I think you know the rest … And when I feel alone, like no one understands what I’m going through, I remember my friends who get it. I never thought I’d be able to do any of this stuff, but I can. Anyone can wear the mask. You could wear the mask. If you didn’t know that before, I hope you do now. Because I’m Spider-Man. And I’m not the only one. Not by a long shot.”

question: Opinions on the Avangers?
answer:
Tony/Dad -

I love my dad he’s truely the world’s greatest defender - Peter

He’s pretty cool, my 2nd favorite tbh - Harley

Steve -

Fuck him, I respect him, but he really hurt my dad - Peter

I pretty much feel the same way Pete does - Harley

Thor -

I might have a crush on him, just a little one, can you blame me? - Peter

I’m jealous, he’s not allowed near my baby boy (jk) he’s pretty cool tho - Harley

Clint -

Literally so fucking bad ass and nice I’m upset at him though he betrayed us - Peter

I haven’t gotten to meet him - Harley

Natasha -

She’s intimidating, but actually really sweet and funny when you get to know her and she’s really badass I can’t believe she betrayed us though - Peter

I haven’t gotten to meet her, but she does scare me - Harley

Bruce -

Uncle Bruce is so smart he’s my idol and I love him so much and I love working with him in the labs - Peter

I think he’s really smart and cool, if not a nervous mess some times - Harley

Spider-man -

His a fucking little bitch - Peter

Baby no, he’s my 100% favorite with out a dought no one is cooler and amazing than Spidey - Harley

Rhodey -

Uncle Rhodey! He’s my god father and I love him so so so much! - Peter

He’s really cool, cares a lot about Peter too - Harley

Sam -

I don’t like him, he made my uncle Rhodey get hurt I use to like him tho, we played Mario kart together - Peter

I mean that’s fair and I agree - Harley

Vison -

He’s like a brother to me - Peter

He’s high key scary but pretty cool - Harley

Wanda -

I never really trusted her, but what made me not like her was her going to Steve’s side - Peter

I was never close to her really - Harley

summary: How can ANYONE NOT like him? Of course I like him. I think he’s a good boy, kindhearted, honest...he deserves the world. He’s...
body:
How can ANYONE NOT like him? Of course I like him. I think he’s a good boy, kindhearted, honest…he deserves the world. He’s just a bit…too naive, revealing his secret identity to everyone he crosses paths with.

Come on, look at his face, don’t you want to adopt him, feed him and protect him? I know I don’t show it, but I sure want to.
